Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: For nearly 4 years as Border Czar, #ComradeKamala has overseen a nation-wrecking border invasion. She has allowed at least 20 million illegal aliens into our country, including millions of unvetted fighting-age men from 158 countries.  Just recently, Kamala let in the head of a Peruvian gang who was wanted for 23 murders.On her orders, Border Patrol is being forced to free tens of thousands of illegal aliens from custody week after week. Every day brings another story about innocent Americans being tortured, raped, murdered and massacred by illegal aliens Kamala Harris has set free.
